Class GenericArtifactMultiLineParser

java.lang.Object

      com.collabnet.ccf.core.utils.GenericArtifactMultiLineParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.openadaptor.core.IComponent, org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor, org.openadaptor.core.jmx.Administrable
public class GenericArtifactMultiLineParser
extends org.openadaptor.core.Component
implements org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor

This component will take the content of an XML document (string) line by line and converts the contained XML documents to a Dom4J document. It assumes that the XML documents piped in line by line are all compliant to the Generic Artifact XML schema (at least they should end with ).

jnicolai

xmlDocument

private java.lang.StringBuffer xmlDocument
This string buffer will store the strings line by line until all lines for one XML document have arrived. After this, the content of the buffer will be used to construct an XML document and empty the buffer again.
